text: Aalesunds Handels- og Søfartstidende (The Ålesund Trade and Maritime Journal) was a newspaper published in Ålesund, Norway from 1856 to 1904.Wasberg, Gunnar Christie. 1969. Norsk presse i hundre år: 1820–1920. Oslo: Gyldendal, p. 136. From 1872 to 1876 it was published under the name Aalesunds Tidende (The Ålesund Journal).Tandstad, Bent. 2016. Døden i meieriet – "et mistænkelig dødsfald." NRK (March 26). It was the first newspaper published in Ålesund.Molde bymuseum: Romsdals Budstikke.Romsdals Budstikkes historie 1843–1882. 2010. Rbnett.no. (March 2). The newspaper had a conservative stance. ==References== Category:Defunct newspapers published in Norway Category:Norwegian-language newspapers Category:Mass media in Møre og Romsdal Category:Ålesund Category:Publications established in 1856 Category:Publications disestablished in 1904
